Introduction

This file combines the data available from the run pp16013.

This includes

  • osmolarity
  • OD
  • cumulative ammonia
  • baseflow
  • conductivity
  • pH
  • Temp

I used k-fold Cross-Validation to predict the biggest influence on the variables. We get a relationship between the following:

  • temperature and baseflow

  • osmolarity and ammonia amount

  • OD vs osmolarity

  • lnOD vs osmolarity
